OL,5, An elderly couple have told how they   
OL,6, fought off an armed robber from their  
OL,7, family-run Manchester jewellery shop.  
OL,9,FMalcolm Abelson, 78, and his wife      
OL,10,FElise, 73, said "the adrenaline kicked 
OL,11,Fin" when they confronted the man as he 
OL,12,Ftried to steal a necklace and diamond  
OL,13,Fbracelet.                              
OL,15,FDuring a scuffle the robber attempted  
OL,16,Fto hit Mr Abelson with a claw hammer   
OL,17,Fbefore he was overpowered.             
OL,19,F"He must have thought two old people   
OL,20,Fwere an easy target," Mrs Abelson said.
